<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:16:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中方谴责缅甸总领事馆遇袭事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国外交部发言人表示，中国谴责周一针对中国驻曼德勒领事馆的袭击，并敦促缅甸当局尽一切努力逮捕肇事者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾任命总统顾问为APEC峰会代表</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</link><description>台湾总统府周一表示，已任命赖清德总统的一名高级顾问作为今年秘鲁亚太经合组织峰会的特使，这是台湾和中国大陆共同参加的少数国际论坛之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia 获得为比亚迪位于土耳其的第二家欧洲工厂供货的协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-secures-deal-supply-byds-second-european-factory-turkey-2024-10-21/</link><description>按收入计算，全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周一表示，比亚迪已选择该公司为其位于土耳其的第二家欧洲工厂供货。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:29:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-secures-deal-supply-byds-second-european-factory-turkey-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>联合国 COP16 谈判中世界在 2030 年自然目标方面落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</link><description>近 200 个国家齐聚哥伦比亚卡利，参加为期两周的联合国生物多样性峰会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，大都会人寿正在洽谈以 10 亿至 15 亿美元收购 PineBridge 在中国以外的资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/metlife-talks-buy-pinebridges-ex-china-assets-1-bln-15-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-10-21/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，总部位于纽约的大都会人寿保险公司正在就收购 PineBridge Investments 在中国境外的资产进行深入谈判，交易价值可能为 10 亿至 15 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/metlife-talks-buy-pinebridges-ex-china-assets-1-bln-15-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia与中国比亚迪和小米达成新供应协议，股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-parts-supplier-forvia-posts-slightly-lower-q3-sales-2024-10-21/</link><description>法国汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周一表示，已与中国汽车制造商比亚迪和小米达成新协议，导致其股价上涨近 10%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 05:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-parts-supplier-forvia-posts-slightly-lower-q3-sales-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港当局称土壤感染导致猴子死亡，第11例死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-say-soil-infection-killed-monkeys-11th-dies-2024-10-21/</link><description>当局表示，类鼻疽是一种细菌感染，导致香港动物园至少 9 只猴子死亡，周末又有两只猴子死亡，过去一周猴子总数达到 11 只。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 02:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-say-soil-infection-killed-monkeys-11th-dies-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市本周开局不温不火，但黄金、比特币大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-21/</link><description>继上周强劲上涨后，周一全球股市以不温不火的姿态开启了本周的开局，而对唐纳德·特朗普赢得即将到来的美国总统大选的押注增加，帮助比特币和黄金创下新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 02:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国上市公司争相利用央行资金购买股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-listed-companies-rush-tap-central-bank-funding-share-purchases-2024-10-21/</link><description>根据交易所备案文件，在中国人民银行启动 420 亿美元融资计划几天后，已有 20 多家中国上市公司宣布计划利用央行特别贷款购买股票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:27:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-listed-companies-rush-tap-central-bank-funding-share-purchases-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国下调主要贷款利率以支持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</link><description>作为振兴经济一揽子刺激措施的一部分，上个月降低了其他政策利率，中国周一按照预期在月度定价中下调了基准贷款利率。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>军演结束一周后，美国和加拿大海军驶​​过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canadian-navies-sail-through-taiwan-strait-week-after-war-games-2024-10-20/</link><description>周日，一艘美国和一艘加拿大军舰一起驶过敏感的台湾海峡，距离中国在台湾进行新一轮军演不到一周，北京谴责这次任务具有“破坏性”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canadian-navies-sail-through-taiwan-strait-week-after-war-games-2024-10-20/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国加强了对两用物品的出口管制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boosts-export-controls-dual-use-items-state-media-says-2024-10-19/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周六报道，中国国务院总理李强已签署国务院令，公布所谓两用物项出口管制条例，该条例将于 2024 年 12 月 1 日生效。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 11:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boosts-export-controls-dual-use-items-state-media-says-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国外交大臣承诺与中国关系保持“一致性”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-secretary-pledges-consistency-relations-with-china-2024-10-19/</link><description>英国外交大臣大卫·拉米周六表示，随着伦敦寻求在新工党政府领导下重置与北京的关系，企业希望与中国的贸易保持“稳定和明确”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 08:14:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-secretary-pledges-consistency-relations-with-china-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平敦促导弹部队增强威慑和作战能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-missile-troops-boost-deterrence-combat-capabilities-2024-10-19/</link><description>中国官方媒体周六报道称，国家主席习近平周四视察了中国人民解放军火箭军的一个旅，敦促部队增强“威慑和作战能力”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-missile-troops-boost-deterrence-combat-capabilities-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>无人机制造商大疆就中国军方名单起诉五角大楼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-dronemaker-dji-sues-pentagon-over-chinese-military-listing-2024-10-19/</link><description>全球最大的无人机制造商表示，这一指定对其造成了财务损失。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 00:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-dronemaker-dji-sues-pentagon-over-chinese-military-listing-2024-10-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>